Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文化祭即将开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.20,0:01:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学校充满了热闹的气氛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.91,0:01:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们1年D班自然也不例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通过了卫生检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.78,0:01:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们“饭团亭”得以顺利开张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.42,0:01:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过为了慎重起见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.06,0:01:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次征询有关饭团材料的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.59,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饭团…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像跟我挺有缘的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.83,0:02:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了！就做三色饭团如何!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.20,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一个饭团里放三种材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会很受欢迎的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不错啊 很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学 最好不要哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.35,0:02:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把咸鲑鱼子、葱、味噌和梅干放在一起好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恶～恶心死了～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最恶心的是你的个性吧…章鱼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛把铁管带来学校啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干脆举办饭团战斗吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1对1 没有任何限制 一招分胜负！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是喷血或是手脱臼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以饭团为名的战斗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.97,0:02:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驳回！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.08,0:02:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…用“没中”好不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没中？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.55,0:02:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是买三送一的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过第四个放的很可能是特别的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.79,0:02:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是“没中”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赞成！意见不错哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你们都听他的意见!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有什么听不听的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你的意见太奇怪了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.03,0:03:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里奇怪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.67,0:03:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁会为了饭团打得全身是血？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是遗憾啊 夹夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要叫我夹夹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系嘛～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必须去出席干部会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有关材料的采买就麻烦大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有件事情想请教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希～有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 由希～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.43,0:03:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 猫咪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么时候跑进来的？哪里来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道啊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！那只猫是怎么搞的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.68,0:03:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧 你的举动才奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来 那家伙的个性还真差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这还用说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟王子刚好相反…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.10,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹真的很喜欢高的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你每次都突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.21,0:04:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好啊 小猫咪 好可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很有猫咪缘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.82,0:04:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁知道啊 是它自己靠过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戌是狗 子是老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好高兴哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高兴你个头啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前和乐罗在山上散步的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.69,0:04:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被几十只猪包围 还以为会被吃掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么 只是有点担心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像很生气…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.11,0:04:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不打算参加文化祭的准备吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没去有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有由希在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切就搞定了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.09,0:05:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家只信赖他一个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从以前就是这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的头脑又好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又会掌握要领 人缘也很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身旁的人都会自然地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.33,0:05:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认同他的才能而尊敬他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就拿学武来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先学的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.98,0:05:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是现在却是他比较强…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼠年生的小孩真的比较“特别”呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 真“特别”…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起来猫年的小孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猫年的小孩就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猫年的小孩就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听了就不爽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.52,0:05:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要把那家伙比下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.90,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为阿夹他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那种容易和人相处的类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.44,0:06:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于他是不属于十二生肖的自然体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.98,0:06:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此能很自然地和“普通”人相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.28,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很想像他一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.39,0:06:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然…草摩同学羡慕阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.33,0:06:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而夹反而羡慕草摩同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.73,0:06:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为互相羡慕 反而处不来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.88,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么人都要羡慕别人呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.09,0:06:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么都不会发觉自己的优点呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有饭团店的味道罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、早安 你每天都这么早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么 很平常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 那是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韭菜饭团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛做这种东西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.41,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个…这是有关文化祭没中的饭团所做的研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.92,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有没有什么好的建议呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饭团上面放鲑鱼或是鳕鱼卵不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 我自己做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 你好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.00,0:07:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你捏饭团的手法好厉害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了！真令人意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.44,0:07:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修行期间都是我自己做饭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.74,0:07:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是手法熟练跟好吃是不一样的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过…要是让潜心修行做寿司的人看到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会很羡慕你那种熟练的捏饭团技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁会做那种修行啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.22,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 怎么会有这种奇怪的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉害的话就是厉害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你自己没有察觉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是黏在你的背上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.28,0:08:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如每个人的优点 就像是饭团的梅干一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.38,0:08:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个梅干就黏在背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个世上每个人的背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.55,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都黏了各种形状、各种口味的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是因为黏在背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以无法知道这些梅干的好处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得自己一无是处…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一堆白米而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实根本不是这么一回事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.94,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背上就黏着梅干呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之所以会羡慕别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.12,0:09:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为看到别人背上的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.82,0:09:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到了 我确实看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹背上有…了不起的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学很棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹你也很棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不知道你怎么会有这种鬼想法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会用梅干来比喻我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.21,0:09:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真、真是抱歉 那用鲑鱼来比喻好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.61,0:09:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 不好意思 都怪我胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.32,0:09:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的背上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.25,0:09:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也黏着梅干哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.67,0:09:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过是很小的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小梅干很好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常～非常～小的梅干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.08,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的！或许现在就有人羡慕我呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.85,0:10:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羡慕我自己没有注意到的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要这么想的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.92,0:10:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会想要一点一点的努力看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文化祭当天来临罗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 这个台子歪歪的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.77,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别注意这么细微的事啦 猫痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对嘛 猫痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.74,0:10:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要没坏就行了嘛 猫痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你们一直猫痴猫痴的叫个不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我当傻瓜吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.85,0:10:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你嘴巴很坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.92,0:10:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过你是个很喜欢动物的好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对个头啦！你们这些家伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都对他改观了 真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一回来就吵吵闹闹 真是吵的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.43,0:10:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过…没想到他会那么坦率的回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.33,0:10:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是难得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.74,0:10:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学是草摩同学 阿夹是阿夹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由‧希～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学姊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.45,0:11:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我们有礼物要送给你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学园祭的时候希望你一定要穿这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.95,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可是我们合买的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特别为由希订做的哦～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味道如何呀～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.58,0:11:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢光临～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢光临！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇～卖得很好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好是饮食摊位第一名哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为本田同学捏的饭团好吃嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？才、才不是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个猫饭团也很可爱哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.30,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对班上生意最有贡献的人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！不要乱拍照啦～～～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.44,0:12:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希会不高兴哦～～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 他真的是…太可爱了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.64,0:12:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶 客人都是冲着草摩同学来的呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.08,0:12:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…我是不是做了什么事惹草摩同学不高兴…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.29,0:12:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别理他啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.32,0:12:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他被迫穿女装 恼羞成怒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.73,0:12:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙对自己的女生相非常排斥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.53,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 你好像女孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.07,0:12:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？阿夹 你认识他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别一个人到处转来转去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希和阿夹都很有朝气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希的朋友耶～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帅呆了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.96,0:12:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好 我是草摩红叶 这位是草摩波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是由希和阿夹的亲戚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.27,0:13:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 红叶就算了 为什么连波鸟这家伙都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.30,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来 莫非这两个人也是十二生肖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 用力地深呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.74,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟是医生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.75,0:13:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用不着在这里诊疗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经约好一个月要检诊一次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,检诊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学 你有哪里不舒服吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…啊 没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希的气管不太好 小时候经常发作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.36,0:13:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然长大之后变得健壮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.40,0:13:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过为了慎重起见还是要检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是本田透吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.24,0:13:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 请多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此…真的是个普通女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦！不能爬到台子上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在干什么啊！ 笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.35,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、不好了 我失陪一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.45,0:14:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们来做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要抱怨去对慊人说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.16,0:14:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人知道有文化祭很想过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.50,0:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过他发烧到39度 被医生拦了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才会代替他来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.14,0:14:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而红叶也跟着过来凑热闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个都是凑热闹的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真的要凑热闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不会选在人比较少的傍晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.58,0:14:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧 我们不是来对本田透下手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.15,0:14:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不那么做是慊人下的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在这里看什么！\N呜啊～～阿夹打我～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.70,0:14:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 是小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.43,0:14:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是小透吧 本田透！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.33,0:14:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是、我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶…是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 你已经记得我的名字啦？好高兴哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 以后请多多指教哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.21,0:15:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 小透 你知道十二生肖的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了 那我可以尽情的抱你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.08,0:15:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下！小色鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.39,0:15:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在小透面前变身应该没关系吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也看场合吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.39,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他果然也是十二生肖之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是看小透可爱打算一个人独占是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.83,0:15:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 你是不是每天都抱着她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋！谁、谁做哪种事啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有机可乘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.00,0:15:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.70,0:15:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆炸吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.44,0:15:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.74,0:15:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？那只兔子是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是红叶的衣服吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧！发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.75,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么红叶会把衣服扔在这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还有兔子…哪里冒出来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太奇怪了！你说说话呀 本田同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来我才奇怪呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男生还做这种打扮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乱讲 你是最棒的！草摩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你真的是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会把你让给别人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 很适合你呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从哪个角度看都是女生嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有自信！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 草摩同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牺牲自己来引起别人注意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.04,0:16:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个死小孩 看看自己干的好事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禁足一个星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是、可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两个好可怕～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少在那边跟女孩子撒娇～～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.95,0:16:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 还好这次多亏了由希转移了他们的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！卖弄风骚本来就是他的兴趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想飞得更高一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.66,0:16:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死老鼠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.13,0:16:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶…你要多留神才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.23,0:16:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个爱惹事的小鬼 差不多该回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要回去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家还想跟小透说话呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.57,0:16:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用不着那么赶啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.44,0:16:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引起骚动就要马上回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是事先说好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟真是无趣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赶快滚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…忘记一件重要的事了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 夹 你们站在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.66,0:16:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简洁地回答我的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1加1等于多少？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.30,0:17:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人要我帮你们两个照张相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍了一张不错的合照！再见了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.97,0:17:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟～～～等一下～～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果还是没弄清楚波鸟的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是不是十二生肖之一呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟透了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是这副模样的相片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被慊人看到了 不晓得他会怎么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学 你会感冒的！你的气管…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受不了这副模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是大家都很喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男生被说可爱有什么值得高兴的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.24,0:17:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思…我也觉得很可爱呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不想让你看到我这副丑态…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.55,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像个白痴似的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然应该拒绝她们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.82,0:18:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 妈妈说我很可爱的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.80,0:18:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得很高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 好可爱哟～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的非常非常高兴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.61,0:18:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…爱情的表现…虽然妈妈她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.61,0:18:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也不会这样说我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以这也意味着大家在说“喜欢你”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.42,0:18:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…这个…没有什么其它的含意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.99,0:18:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听你说我可爱居然有种高兴的感觉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.53,0:18:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了学姊她们 再奉送一段时间好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.14,0:18:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 你能先帮我拿下来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.41,0:18:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,头发被钮扣钩住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.65,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这套洋装穿和脱都很麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是你来穿的话一定很适合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我也很向往呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像公主一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是你穿的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相机抢过来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.32,0:19:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆 根本没机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于波鸟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有机会见到他的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好避免和他独处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.96,0:19:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.33,0:19:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…并不是波鸟本身有什么不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.34,0:19:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你说过我以前泄漏真面目的事吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.27,0:19:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时把所有人的记忆消除的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是波鸟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我有些担心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须先提醒你才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.46,0:20:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1年D班本田透同学 1年D班本田透同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请立即到一楼谘询室来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重复一次 1年D班本田…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在叫我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先去看看再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.87,0:20:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.11,0:20:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你找过来 真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹就不用说了 要是由希在场的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无法好好跟你说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.48,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在只有我们两个独处！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有点冒昧 不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.25,0:20:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次放假的时候到草摩本家来玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.29,0:20:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有些事情想告诉你 很重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然 不能对由希他们说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.40,0:20:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没有权利拒绝 你明白我的意思吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.21,0:21:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该、该怎么办才好呢…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是拒绝的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的记忆就会被消除吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可、可是…或许真的是很重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.75,0:21:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈说不能随便怀疑别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必担心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.19,0:21:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟不会侵犯你的啦 我会在旁边守护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.43,0:21:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以一定要来哦 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.03,0:21:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透是女孩子耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.90,0:21:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟两个男生单独相处会害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 小透 要来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.84,0:21:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶要我去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.11,0:21:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就放心多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.34,0:21:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟突然要我到本家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.32,0:21:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还要瞒着紫吴、草摩同学和阿夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.89,0:21:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟有什么事要对我说呢…

